        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="主题安装"><a href="#主题安装" class="headerlink" title="主题安装"></a>主题安装</h3><h1 id="nmp安装"><a href="#nmp安装" class="headerlink" title="nmp安装"></a>nmp安装</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm i hexo-theme-anzhiyu</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="应用主题"><a href="#应用主题" class="headerlink" title="应用主题"></a>应用主题</h1><p>打开 Hexo 根目录下的 config.yml, 找到以下配置项，把主题改为anzhiyu</p><pre><code># Extensions## Plugins: https://hexo.io/plugins/## Themes: https://hexo.io/themes/theme: anzhiyu<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">### 安装pug和stylus渲染插件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save# 无法安装可以使用cnpm进行安装npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save --registry=http://registry.npmmirror.com<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">### 覆盖配置</span><br><span class="line">覆盖配置可以使主题配置放置在 anzhiyu 目录之外，避免在更新主题时丢失自定义的配置。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">通过 Npm 安装主题的用户可忽略，其他用户建议学习使用。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">macos/linux 在博客根目录运行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>cp -rf ./themes/anzhiyu/_config.yml ./_config.anzhiyu.yml<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">本地启动hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>hexo clhexo ghexo s```</code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
